    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052990/extras/f816cbd58b03f024c8151663cb674570.poster.avif?t=1753341768\" width=620 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052990/extras/f816cbd58b03f024c8151663cb674570.webm?t=1753341768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052990/extras/f816cbd58b03f024c8151663cb674570.mp4?t=1753341768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你唯吾独尊，号令天下，定夺万民悲喜，统一国之权。<br><br>你看似拥有一切，内心却尽是虚无。<br><br>你是朱国德高望重的帝王，尊号为弘。作为朱国最尊贵的人，你却经历着莫大的痛苦。在亲历你的母后，也就是上一任君主的离世后，你最深爱的皇后也不幸薨逝。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052990/extras/9d56a48588bdf6211a1dfa8197c8efaf.poster.avif?t=1753341768\" width=620 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052990/extras/9d56a48588bdf6211a1dfa8197c8efaf.webm?t=1753341768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052990/extras/9d56a48588bdf6211a1dfa8197c8efaf.mp4?t=1753341768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>不堪内心的痛苦折磨，你选择召唤妖怪寻求帮助。这群禁忌生物来自遥远的北方，它们危险强大，喜欢攫取人类的灵魂。它们将会协助你解决王国困境，服从你的意志，为你的子民谋取福祉。<br><br>不过切记，你不是这个世上唯一的统治者，在朱国走向繁荣发展的过程中，如何平衡子民需求与他国交易将是你不可避免的难题。当帝国发展到了顶峰，你还将面临新的选择：继续带领自己的国家与子民走向更加昌盛的未来，还是利用妖怪的力量，献祭整个帝国以此复活心爱的皇后。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052990/extras/e712fea5c27777043685ec7046aa1d96.poster.avif?t=1753341768\" width=620 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052990/extras/e712fea5c27777043685ec7046aa1d96.webm?t=1753341768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052990/extras/e712fea5c27777043685ec7046aa1d96.mp4?t=1753341768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>带有东亚、东南亚神话元素的帝国资源管理与模拟游戏。<br></li><li>召唤各具特色的妖怪们来协助你履行帝王的职责。<br></li><li>与妖怪们建立关系，增强它们的能力，以此成为强大的盟友或更具价值的祭品。<br></li><li>与其他统治者合作以实现你的终极目标，或与他们共同选择一条不同的道路。<br></li><li>故事的发展走向将根据你的选择发生变化。<br></li><li>恢弘的配乐为你打造身临其境的游玩体验。<br></li><li>2D与3D的视觉效果一同打造迷人的亚洲水墨风。</li></ul>",
